      "rationale": "Nonlinear static analysis uses Newton-Raphson iteration with residual convergence criterion 1e-6. All 11 construct simulations converged without divergence or excessive substep bisection. Energy balance verified. Achieved level 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Use error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Documented simulation workflow with independent review of boundary conditions, material assignments, and load application. Required level 2.",
      "rationale": "Simulation setup reviewed by a second analyst independent of the model developer. Boundary conditions, material properties, and contact definitions verified against ASTM F1717 test configuration. Discrepancies resolved prior to results extraction. Achieved level 2."
